# HobiHobby — Project Context

## Product Stage
Solo founder, early MVP. Live on Firebase Hosting at hobihobby.com.
Quality over speed. No hard launch deadline.

## Active Sprint: Sprint 2 — AI Hook

### Sprint 2 Scope
- AI Hobby Discovery Quiz — 7 questions → Gemini → ranked recommendations
- AI Hobby Coach — WhatsApp-style chat via `hobbyCoach` Cloud Function
- Tutorial summarization — `summarizeTutorial` Cloud Function (backend only, no UI)

### Sprint 2 Rules
- Do NOT build community features, maps, payments, or streaks yet
- All AI calls go through Firebase Cloud Functions — never expose API keys in frontend
- Cloud Functions use the **v2 SDK** (`firebase-functions/v2/https`)
- AI model: `gemini-2.0-flash` for quiz + coach, `gemini-2.0-flash-lite` for summarization

## Architecture Decisions (Locked)
- **Firebase-native only.** No Express backend in production, no MongoDB, no Mongoose. Firestore is the single source of truth.
- **No micro-frontends.** Legacy `root-config/` and `micro-frontends/` scaffolding exists — ignore it. All active dev is in `web/`.
- **All AI calls through Cloud Functions.** Gemini API key lives only in Firebase Functions secrets.
- **Cloud Functions v2 SDK only.** Import from `firebase-functions/v2/https`, not the legacy v1 API.
- **Firebase Hosting only.** Vercel is decommissioned.

